TUTORIAL

    This is how you can start your own webapp with Katokorbo:
    
    1. Put your webapp.war on the web.
    
    2. Create a katokorbo.properties file with following properties:
    
        title=Your application title
        port=9065
        warUrl=http://your-domain/webapp.war
        version=1.0
      
       Optionally add more properties:
      
        windowIconUrl=http://your-domain/webapp-icon-64.png
        eulaUrl=http://your-domain/webapp-eula.txt
        
    3. Put this properties file on the web.
    
    4. Download https://github.com/downloads/witek/katokorbo/katokorbo.jar
    
    5. Start Katokorbo:
    
        java -jar katokorbo.jar http://your-domain/katokorbo.properties
